# 二. codex安装使用：


1.Node.js（版本22或更高）安装后， 安装codex： npm install -g @openai/codex， 验证成功：


![image2026-3-19_17-49-29.png](test.assets/image2026-3-19_17-49-29.png)


codex 配置文件位于 <用户目录>/.codex目录下编辑config.toml文件，大模型就选最新的gpt-5.4，添加或修改：


model_provider = "ylscode"


model = "gpt-5.4"
model_reasoning_effort = "high"


network_access = "enabled"
disable_response_storage = true


approval_policy = "untrusted"
sandbox_mode    = "read-only"
personality = "pragmatic"


env_key = "OPENAI_API_KEY"


[model_providers.ylscode]
name = "ylscode"
base_url = "[https://code.ylsagi.com/codex](https://code.ylsagi.com/codex)"
wire_api = "responses"
requires_openai_auth = true


[windows]
sandbox = "elevated"


[projects.'C:\Users\daiyunfei']
trust_level = "trusted"


[projects.'\\?\G:\test']
trust_level = "trusted"


[features]
multi_agent = true


[mcp_servers.figma]
url = "[https://mcp.figma.com/mcp](https://mcp.figma.com/mcp)"


2.下载安装window版本codex


下载地址：[https://openai.com/zh-Hans-CN/codex/](https://openai.com/zh-Hans-CN/codex/)


启动后输入key登录后选择指定工程目录：


